NOTIFY FAILURE ABEND ALERT(REMD)
NOTIFY OVERDUE MAILBOX(BRMDLY)
EXITCODE 0-1 SUCCESS

AS400_JOB BRMDLYMNT.LVPROD
  RESOURCE ADD(1,TAPMLB02) HOLD
  AGENT LVPROD
  COMMAND CYBROBOT2 BRMDLYMNT
  JOBQ CAWAAGENT.CYBESPJOBS
  RUN DAILY
   DELAYSUB 17.30
    DUEOUT EXEC 18.00
     IF TODAY('JAN 28 2018') THEN JOBATTR HOLD
  RELEASE ADD(BRMDLYSAVF.LVPROD)
ENDJOB

